Museveni held a one-hour meeting with visiting Islamic spiritual
leader Aga Khan here today on economic cooperation.
</P>
<P>
Earlier, he held talks with Ugandan Vice-President Specioza W.
Kazibwe on some social and economic issues.
</P>
<P>
The two sides stressed the importance of continued cooperation
and highlighted the democratic path taken by the Ugandan
government.
</P>
