<HEADLINE> At 11 People Killed in Road Accident in India </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, March 11 (Xinhua) -- At least 11 people were killed
and 38 others injured, ten of them seriously, when a private
transport bus fell into a 300-feet-deep gorge in Himachal state in
northwestern India today.
</P>
<P>
Reports reaching here said that nine of those killed died on
the spot while two succumbed to injuries in hospital. The bus was
carrying over 50 passengers.
</P>
