source said here today.
</P>
<P>
Makwetu, 69, now PAC national chairman, was stripped of his
parliament seat at an extraordinary meeting of the PAC National
Working Committee (NWC) in Johannesburg last Friday while he was
on a tour to Kenya as part of a government delegation.
</P>
