<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, March 10 (Xinhua) -- Third-seed Anke Huber of
Germany was knocked out of the quarter-finals of the Evert Cup
women's tennis tournament by 13th seed Nathalie Tauziat in Indian
Wells on Monday.
</P>
