<HEADLINE> India, France to Enhance Economic Ties </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, March 11 (Xinhua) -- Visiting French Minister of
Agriculture and Food Processing Philippe Vasseur has held
discussions with his Indian counterpart Chaturanan Mishra as well
as other Indian ministers on cooperation in hi-tech areas of
agriculture and food processing.
</P>
<P>
According to local press reports today, during the meetings,
Vasseur said that although some joint ventures existed between
France and India in dairy and aquaculture, new ventures were also
being identified.
