<TEXT>
<P>
ROME, March 10 (Xinhua) -- The Italian Senate has approved a
bill to restore the Leaning Tower of Pisa and is providing 12
billion liras (about 7.1 million U.S. dollars) toward the cost
over the next two years.
</P>
