<HEADLINE> National Retail Sales Price Index Stable in January </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, March 11 (Xinhua) -- The national retail sales price
index stayed at 103.3 in January, taking the price indes of the
same period of 1996 as 100, according to the latest statistics
from the State Statistics Bureau.
</P>
<P>
The retail sales price index for food stood at 103.5, and that
of textile products 103.4.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, the index of household electrical appliances dropped
to 97, as a result of nation-wide price war throughout January,
and that of daily use articles stood at 103.7.
</P>
