<HEADLINE> "Ice" Drug Seized in East China's Fujian Province </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
FUZHOU, March 11 (Xinhua) -- Police in Zhangzhou City, Fujian
Province, arrested five people suspected of drug manufacture. The
police seized 30.66 kg of "ice" and drug making equipment and
materials on January 5 this year, according to police sources.
</P>
